      • addFiles

        private long addFiles(com.sun.jersey.multipart.FormDataMultiPart formdata,
                      LinkedList<String> files,
                      String attachmentType,
                      String dir,
                      String basename,
                      LinkedList<String> problems)
        addFiles - List of files that are attached to an XML document e.g. image or audio data Given a list of files and a form, add them to the form so that they can be uploaded.
        Parameters:
        formdata - - form to be submitted
        files - - List of files to upload
        attachmentType - - What type of attachment (e.g. image/audio)
        dir - - The base directory from which we search for the attachments
        basename - - Attachment directory will be related to this name, either dir/basename/attachmentType or dir/basename-attachementType
        problems - - An list of strings. Any files that cannot be found will be added to this.
        Returns:
        - # of bytes in the files that could be found.
